    <div class="comment--content">
      <p>You may want to try Lindsey Shere&#39;s Almond Torte (from Chez Panisse Desserts) &#8212; it looks much like the one in your snapshots.  It&#39;s beautifully moist, dense with almond paste, and yet it&#39;s still light.  I&#39;ve tried to make it somewhat my own by adding the zest of an orange &#8212; the flavors go together very well. </p>
